column1: 2007 South Dakota State Powerlifting and Bench Press Championships
Men's Nationals -St. Louis MO - Greg Wagner
Women's Nationals - Killeen, TX - Diann Nelson, Julie Zohner, Katie Kneifl, Deb Kullerd
Master Nationals -  Milwaukee, WI  -  Monte Mason, Brent Steinback, Larry Robinson, Ken Leisinger, Marlin Hertz, Joe Kunzman
Note: Any lifter with a legal Individual lift may compete at single lift nationals (ex. Bench Press Nationals, Denver, CO)
For more information on USA Powerlifting and other meets during the year, visit usapowerlifting.com; or the South Dakota site usapl-sd.com.
